snippet.title: "DUSTTRUST X" Underevent Trailer (2/3)
snippet.description:
This trailer was showcased in UNDEREVENT 2024! Be sure to check it out: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ho5jkOfUFtY

From AWESOME GAMES, the team behind GREEN SANS, Underswap Thanatos, Retro Edition and DUSTBELIEF
Follow DUSTTRUST X on Game Jolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/dusttrust/547556

participating in underevent was a great and fun experience, very happy we were given the chance to do this again. this trailer was done months ago though so some things are a bit outdated, check out our latest devlog for uptodate stuff https://gamejolt.com/p/progress-update-4-underevent-xpnfhwym

- Credits - 
DUSTTRUST X by Ari & goinks
DUSTTRUST by DillyWolf

Thumbnail Art by okittsy
Thumbnail by Ari
Trailer & Trailer Editing: Ari
Trailer Contributions: francis.gif, Dendy, RedD7
Music: "Through The Flame (Underevent Cut)" by Nickolas (https://soundcloud.com/nikalt/underevent2024)
